OL,3,CChef calls out customers who leave
OL,4,Cwithout paying #370 bill
OL,6,FAn award-winning chef Gary Usher has
OL,7,Fcalled out customers who left his
OL,8,Frestaurant without paying their #370
OL,9,Fbill.
OL,11,FThe chef and restaurateur, who owns
OL,12,Fthe Elite Bistros group of restaurants
OL,13,Fin the North West including including
OL,14,FKala in Manchester city centre and
OL,15,FHispi in Didsbury, south Manchester,
OL,16,Ftook to social media to share the
OL,17,Fstory.
