OL,3,CChef calls out customers who leave
OL,4,Cwithout paying #370 bill
OL,6,FPosting an excerpt from the end of day
OL,7,Freport from Hispi, on School Lane,
OL,8,Ffrom Monday 20 May, a member of staff
OL,9,Fsaid the party of three did not settle
OL,10,Ftheir #371.80 bill after telling the
OL,11,Fserver they were going outside the
OL,12,Fvenue for a smoke.
OL,14,F"Had a table of 3 walk in to celebrate
OL,15,Ftheir dad's birthday," the post read.
OL,17,F"They built up a tab of #371.80 and
OL,18,Fwalked out without paying. I apologise
OL,19,Fprofusely, I had all faith that they
OL,20,Fwere going for a cigarette."
