OL,3,CChef calls out customers who leave
OL,4,Cwithout paying #370 bill
OL,6,FGary's followers shared his
OL,7,Ffrustration. One said: "So basically
OL,8,Fthe restaurant opened for the night
OL,9,Fwith little profit to show now. Must
OL,10,Fbe demoralising."
OL,12,FThe chef replied: "Yep."
OL,14,F"So sorry to hear this Gary - cant
OL,15,Fimagine what this must feel like for a
OL,16,Fbusiness owner trying to make a
OL,17,Fliving. Just looked at your bistro
OL,18,Fonline and looks amazing! Will be sure
OL,19,Fto make a visit when next over in
OL,20,FManc," another added.
