OL,6,FStockport pub The Petersgate Tap
OL,7,Fresponded: "Gutting Gary - what is
OL,8,Fwrong with people these days??"
OL,10,FOne person asked: "Will we end up at
OL,11,Fthe point where, like a hotel, you
OL,12,Fstart to take a holding/pending amount
OL,13,Fon the card when we enter? I would be
OL,14,Fhappy for this to happen."
OL,16,FIn April, Gary was after a negative
OL,17,Freview targeted a waitress.
OL,19,FThe one-star review diner described a
OL,20,F'miserable' experience and the waiting
OL,21,Fstaff's attitude as 'horrible'.
